plot: Vicki gets confronted by her son Michael for not letting him know about her most recent procedure. The conflict between Tamra and Gina continues at Emily's Turkish coffee cup reader gathering. When Kelly helps Gina move into her casita, she questions if Shannon may be manipulating the Tamra-Gina rift. Emily throws Gina a 34th birthday party, and instead of attending, Tamra, Shannon and Vicki throw an old lady party.
